<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <?eclipse version="3.4"?> <plugin> <extension-point id="de.jabc.cinco.plugin.executor" name="de.jabc.cinco.plugin.executor" schema="schema/de.jabc.cinco.plugin.executor.exsd"/>
